sections.heading: Sections; exclusive; applicability of other law
sections.text: Sections 70-701 to 70-738 are complete in themselves, and shall be controlling. The provisions of any other law of this state, except as provided in said sections, shall not apply to a corporation organized under said sections.SourceLaws 1937, c. 50, ยง
